.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
City: edinburgh, boston, london, miami, liverpool
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, volleyball, soccer, snowboarding, surfing

1. the english is the person who likes red
2. the spanish is the person who's sport is cycling
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes green
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's sport is surfing
7. the person traveling to boston is the person who likes yellow
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball
11. the person traveling to boston is to the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding
12. the person traveling to miami is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person traveling to liverpool
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| City		|     boston	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| miami	|   parliament	|
| Sport		|     volleyball	|     snowboarding	|     surfing	|     cycling	|     soccer	|
